se.miun.itm.input.util

Class Q

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.miun.itm.input.util.Q

  • public class Q
extends java.lang.Object
    A help class that contains all the identifiers of objects and concepts used in InPUT. References should all point here, and none for InPUT meaningful String should be solely defined in another class.
    Author:
    Felix Dobslaw, Stefan Karlsson
